## Vitest

The template is configured with Vitest test runner. It is configured so that
the tests are expacted to be under src/ and collected in `__tests__/`
subdirectories. Read more about Vitest [here](https://vitest.dev/guide/).

{{#if optionData.reactTestingLibrary}}
### Setup file

There is also a simple setup file `testSetup.ts`. It uses `cleanup()` function
from `@testing-library/react` to cleanup after each test.
{{/if}}
